03T09:00:17.000Z","msg":"同意  如果有禮貌講句: 有冇位可以讓阿婆坐下<br />\n一定會有人讓 但見人後生大大聲屌人老馮比個位你就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你又知我冇唔舒服?"},{"pid":"28f754863cdab2cb5ebb95ef55a350f2319c189e","tid":1136581,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T10:27:16.000Z","msg":"其實我好撚憎電視某廣告，乜嘢叫人將讓座嘅藉口通通踢走。根本就係將有需要人士嘅種類收窄，然後限死人只可以讓座俾嗰四種人。其他人話知你就死都要讓座。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8419b018d1f9f70855426dc8f53b479b3b052c","tid":1136581,"uid":61115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bacbada3a5c16c85371de435e8d58ac6f2f939ea","tid":1136581,"uid":251510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"815e9275c78cc010b1ab0d075d0ba30dd750ea69","tid":1136581,"uid":40750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d599de0db0cd18064363a936a6f09ccb5176dfd","tid":1136581,"uid":251510,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:17:02.000Z","msg":"以前冇關愛座，好似個社會氣氛和諧好多。廢老、大肚婆唔會批鬥人。而好多人都好樂意讓座，而家就完全調轉曬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"無&gt;有&gt;無 既好恐怖<br />\n我覺得會周位叫人起身多過變番以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:唔會理，照坐，比人屌9我會問佢知唔知咩叫個請字"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"咁你又講得啱，呢個社會已經返唔會轉頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"批鬥文化已經係返唔到轉頭<br />\n總有一班人以正義屌人/拍人片為樂<br />\n<br />\n真正解決問題係要擴大關愛座規模同規範化<br />\n兩者缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n係最接近月台lip既位置 整個兩個關愛車卡<br />\n一般人可以入去 但唔可以坐關愛卡坐位<br />\n有需要既人直接去關愛卡坐<br />\n無權亦無需要批鬥其他車卡乘客<br />\n繁忙上下班時間例外<br />\n <br />\n兩卡都唔夠位要批鬥既<br />\n就4種有需要人士係卡內互鬥<br />\n<br />\n巴士就難搞d"}]}